item.title: CVE-2023-25761|2023-10-24T12:48:53.961Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20junit%20plugin
item.description: Jenkins JUnit Plugin 1166.va_436e268e972 and earlier does not escape test case class names in JavaScript expressions, resulting in a stored cross-site scripting (XSS) vulnerability exploitable by attackers able to control test case class names in the JUnit resources processed by the plugin.
